content.content:
The accounts payable balance as at 30 September 2022 mainly entailed consulting fees to Business Management Consulting Co. of CNY2.3M and logistics services to Logistics Development Co., Ltd. of CNY8.3M.

SUMMARY: Used entities 'Business Management Consulting Co.' (CNY2.3M) and 'Logistics Development Co., Ltd.' (CNY8.3M), which constitute the majority of the total CNY11.8M accounts payable.
